nodes.text: Fleecs was a female Weequay who was part of a crew led by the Abednedo Telsla. She often got into arguments with fellow crewman, Belk. After taking over Tomarian's Annual Festival of Light Gala at his theater, Telsla sent Fleecs to go search for anyone else in the theater. Fleecs came back empty handed.The Abednedo then ordered Fleecs to tie up Tomarian.
